%N A025936 Expansion of g.f. 1/((1-2*x)*(1-3*x)*(1-5*x)*(1-12*x)).
%H A025936 Vincenzo Librandi, <a href="/A025936/b025936.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..900</a>
%H A025936 <a href="/index/Rec#order_04">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, signature (22,-151,402,-360).
%F A025936 a(n) = 22*a(n-1)-151*a(n-2)+ 402*a(n-3)- 360*a(n-4), n>3. - _Harvey P. Dale_, May 07 2012
%F A025936 a(n) = 96*12^n/35 +3^(n+1)/2 -2^(n+2)/15 -5^(n+3)/42. - _R. J. Mathar_, May 22 2013
%F A025936 E.g.f.: exp(2*x)*(576*exp(10*x) - 625*exp(3*x) + 315*exp(x) - 56)/210. - _Stefano Spezia_, Oct 28 2023
%F A025936 a(n) = 3^(n+1)-2^(n+1)+17*a(n-1)-60*a(n-2). - _Vincenzo Librandi_, Apr 24 2026
%t A025936 CoefficientList[Series[1/((1-2*x)*(1-3*x)*(1-5*x)*(1-12*x)),{x,0,30}],x] (* _Harvey P. Dale_, May 07 2012 *)
